
Privacy Policy (English) 

Last updated: [May 16, 2025]

Your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines what data Max collects and how it is used.

Data Collection

Max may collect the following data: User IDs and server IDs Message content only when required for core features (e.g. moderation, commands) Server configuration settings 

Data Usage

The data is only used to provide and improve the functionality of Max. We do not sell, share, or use your data for advertising. 

Data Storage

Data is stored securely and only for as long as necessary to provide the service. Sensitive data is never stored unless essential to a feature and with user consent. 

Third-Party Sharing

We do not share any data with third parties. 

User Rights

You may request deletion of your data by contacting the bot owner via Discord. 

Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy. Continued use of Max means you accept the current version

